channel.title: Good People
channel.desc: Action 2014 In over their heads with debt, a couple finds unexpected cash in a dead tenant's apartment. Hoping to erase their debts, they keep it, only to be hunted by a ruthless thief who will stop at nothing to get it back. Sam Spruell, Michael Fox, Diarmaid Murtagh, Francis Magee, Omar Sy, Henrik Genz, Marcus Sakey.
